text: Karayevo () is a rural locality (a village) in Yakshimbetovsky Selsoviet, Kuyurgazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 85 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 28 km from Yermolayevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kuyurgazinsky District
title: Karayevo
